  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "ch48-01",
      "text": "L'alerte est là.",
      "imagePrompt": "In a steampunk fortress corridor, brass alarm bells mounted on the wall ring loudly while red warning lights flash on a brass control panel, Avril and Julius facing the viewer with startled expressions. Close-up on the alarm bells, eye-level. Flashing red light mixed with gaslight, alarming and urgent mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "alert",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-02",
      "text": "C'est mécanique.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "alert",
      "speaker": "Narrateur"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-03",
      "text": "L'alerte se répand dans le monde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "alert",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-04",
      "text": "C'est mécanique parce que la machine fonctionne.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "alert",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-05",
      "text": "Il faut agir car l'alerte est mécanique.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "alert",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-06",
      "text": "Ça tape ici.",
      "imagePrompt": "In a gaslit steampunk fortress corridor, Julius faces the viewer with fist raised having just struck a guard, Avril beside him gripping a bundle of pulled cables from a sparking control panel. Medium shot, eye-level. Gaslight from wall sconces mixed with electrical sparks, combative and chaotic mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "hitting",
      "speaker": "Julius"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-07",
      "text": "Le câble est là.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "hitting",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-08",
      "text": "Avril tape le câble.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "hitting",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-09",
      "text": "On a tapé le câble, et ça fonctionne.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "hitting",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-10",
      "text": "Avril tape le câble qui est dans le labo.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "hitting",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-11",
      "text": "Avril maîtrise le réacteur.",
      "imagePrompt": "In the steampunk fortress reactor room, Avril faces the viewer with confident hands on the brass levers of a massive reactor control panel, mastering the complex array of dials and gauges before her. Medium shot, eye-level. Warm gaslight from the reactor glow on brass instruments, empowered and commanding mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "mastery",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-12",
      "text": "Ça étonne le monde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "mastery",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-13",
      "text": "Ça a étonné Avril.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mastery",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-14",
      "text": "On maîtrise le câble.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mastery",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-15",
      "text": "Ça étonne tout le monde.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "mastery",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-16",
      "text": "C'est le cafard.",
      "imagePrompt": "In a gaslit steampunk fortress corridor, Avril faces the viewer slumped against the wall with a weary expression of deep blues, Julius sitting beside her looking dejected, a cockroach crawling on the pipe above them. Medium shot, eye-level. Dim gaslight from a single wall fixture, despondent and exhausted mood.",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "blues",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-17",
      "text": "Avril est amoureuse.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "teaching",
      "group": "blues",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-18",
      "text": "Le cafard arrive, mais Avril est amoureuse.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "blues",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-19",
      "text": "Avril est très amoureuse.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "blues",
      "speaker": "Avril"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-20",
      "text": "Le cafard ne reste pas.",
      "imagePrompt": "",
      "readings": [],
      "type": "flow",
      "group": "blues",
      "speaker": "Paul"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch48-21",
      "text": "On maîtrise l'alerte.",
